{"tid":2142913,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Netflix紀錄片「被害公審」女主角  Daisy Coleman自殺身亡","createTime":"2020-08-06T18:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T05:06:51.000Z","uid":41818,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"3b52bd7e899bb2a41c2d732e913048de4bf3791d","tid":2142913,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:20:32.000Z","msg":"影視串流平台Netflix在2016年推出紀錄片《被害公審》（Audrie &amp; Daisy），講述兩名少女遭性侵後，得不到公平審訊之餘，事後更遭社區及網絡欺凌的真人真事。紀錄片播出後，惹起極大迴響。片中受害人之一Daisy Coleman前日在家自殺身亡，終年23歲。<br />\n<br />\n據Daisy的母親證實，前日她因聯絡不到女兒，於是報警求助，警方登門發現Daisy屍體，但未有透露死因。《被害公審》講述2012年Daisy應同學邀請參加派對，當年只有14歲的她，結果遭17歲學長Matthew Barnett性侵，後者被捕竟獲判無罪，其母認為審判不公，跟被告人的家族政治背景有關。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20200806/1596705394559/%E3%80%9014%E6%AD%B2%E9%81%AD%E6%80%A7%E4%BE%B5%E3%80%91%E3%80%8A%E8%A2%AB%E5%AE%B3%E5%85%AC%E5%AF%A9%E3%80%8B%E5%A5%B3%E4%B8%BB%E8%A7%92daisy-coleman%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20200806%2F1596705394559%2F%25E3%2580%259014%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%2580%25A7%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E3%2580%2591%25E3%2580%258A%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E3%2580%258B%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%25A7%2592daisy-coleman%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E4%25BA%25A1&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOhZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=3dd92334\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20200806%2F1596705394559%2F%25E3%2580%259014%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%2580%25A7%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E3%2580%2591%25E3%2580%258A%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E3%2580%258B%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%25A7%2592daisy-coleman%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E4%25BA%25A1&h=c7e8640c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20200806/1596705394559/%E3%80%9014%E6%AD%B2%E9%81%AD